unt":1,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/yvCX7D33bVp36VmXDRHriQjpZHL.jpg","iso_639_1":null,"iso_3166_1":null,"vote_count":2,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0.166},{"width":1920,"height":1080,"file_path":"/dg3XtamcMTGD7YNzb53XDatPWjx.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0},{"width":3840,"height":2160,"file_path":"/oBToVFkZt7WmT0DkTQ6kP1zSw6C.jpg","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","vote_count":0,"aspect_ratio":1.778,"vote_average":0}]},"enriched_at":"2026-04-21T04:46:27.848+00:00","enrichment_cycle":1,"translations":[{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En la época del Imperio Azteca, Yohualli Coatl, un joven azteca, experimenta una tragedia cuando su padre y líder de la aldea, Toltecatzin, es asesinado por los conquistadores españoles. Yohualli escapa a Tenochtitlán para advertir al rey Moctezuma y a su sumo sacerdote, Yoka, del peligro inminente. Usando el templo de Tzinacan, el dios murciélago, como guarida, Yohualli entrena con su mentor y asistente, Acatzin, desarrollando equipo y armamento para enfrentar la invasión española, proteger el templo de Moctezuma y vengar la muerte de su padre."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"MX","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Aztec Batman: Clash of Empires","runtime":90,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.warnerbros.com/movies/aztec-batman-clash-empires","overview":"In the time of the Aztec empire, tragedy strikes Yohualli Coatl when his father is murdered by Spanish conquistadors. To warn King Moctezuma and his high priest, Yoka, of imminent danger, Yohualli escapes to Tenochtitlán. There, he trains in the temple of the bat god Tzinacan with his mentor, developing equipment and weaponry to confront the Spanish invasion and avenge his father’s death. Along the way, he encounters key figures like the fierce Jaguar Woman and the conquistador Hernán Cortés."},"name":"English","iso_639_1":"en","iso_3166_1":"US","english_name":"English"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En la época del Imperio Azteca, Yohualli Coatl, un joven azteca, experimenta una tragedia cuando su padre y líder de la aldea, Toltecatzin, es asesinado por los conquistadores españoles. Yohualli escapa a Tenochtitlán para advertir al rey Moctezuma y a su sumo sacerdote, Yoka, del peligro inminente. Usando el templo de Tzinacan, el dios murciélago, como guarida, Yohualli entrena con su mentor y asistente, Acatzin, desarrollando equipo y armamento para enfrentar la invasión española, proteger el templo de Moctezuma y vengar la muerte de su padre."},"name":"Español","iso_639_1":"es","iso_3166_1":"ES","english_name":"Spanish"},{"data":{"title":"Aztec Batman: Clash of Empires","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Zur Zeit des Aztekenreiches erlebt der Aztekenjunge Yohualli Coatl eine Tragödie, als sein Vater und Dorfoberhaupt Toltecatzin von den spanischen Konquistadoren ermordet wird. Yohualli flieht nach Tenochtitlan, um König Moctezuma und seinen Hohepriester Yoka vor der drohenden Gefahr zu warnen. Im Tempel des Fledermausgottes Tzinacan trainiert Yohualli mit seinem Mentor und Assistenten Acatzin und entwickelt Ausrüstung und Waffen, um die Invasion der Spanier abzuwehren, Moctezumas Tempel zu schützen und den Tod seines Vaters zu rächen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"In de tijd van het Azteekse rijk ervaart Yohualli Coatl – een jonge Azteekse jongen – een tragedie wanneer zijn vader en dorpsleider, Toltecatzin, wordt vermoord door Spaanse veroveraars. Yohualli ontsnapt naar Tenochtitlan om koning Moctezuma en zijn hogepriester Yoka te waarschuwen voor dreigend gevaar. Met behulp van de tempel van Tzinacan, de vleermuisgod, als schuilplaats, traint Yohualli samen met zijn mentor en assistent Acatzin, waarbij hij uitrusting en wapens ontwikkelt om de invasie van de Spanjaarden het hoofd te bieden, de tempel van Moctezuma te beschermen en de dood van zijn vader te wreken."},"name":"Nederlands","iso_639_1":"nl","iso_3166_1":"NL","english_name":"Dutch"},{"data":{"title":"Batman Azteca: Choque de Impérios","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Em uma ousada releitura da lenda do Batman ambientada no império asteca, um jovem asteca escapa para Tenochtitlán após seu pai ser assassinado por conquistadores espanhóis. Uma vez lá, ele treina no templo do deus morcego Tzinacan e desenvolve armas para vingar a morte do pai. Ao longo do caminho, ele encontra figuras conhecidas, como a Mulher-Onça e o conquistador Hernán Cortés."},"name":"Português","iso_639_1":"pt","iso_3166_1":"BR","english_name":"Portuguese"},{"data":{"title":"Aztec Batman: Clash of Empires","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"À l'époque de l'empire aztèque, Yohualli Coatl est frappé par une tragédie lorsque son père est assassiné par les conquistadors espagnols. Afin d'avertir le roi Moctezuma et son grand prêtre, Yoka, du danger imminent, Yohualli s'enfuit à Tenochtitlán. Là, il s'entraîne dans le temple du dieu chauve-souris Tzinacan avec son mentor, développant des équipements et des armes pour affronter l'invasion espagnole et venger la mort de son père. En chemin, il rencontre des personnages clés tels que la féroce Femme Jaguar et le conquistador Hernán Cortés."},"name":"Français","iso_639_1":"fr","iso_3166_1":"FR","english_name":"French"},{"data":{"title":"阿兹特克蝙蝠侠：帝国冲突","runtime":89,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"这部影片大胆重塑了蝙蝠侠的传奇故事，背景设定在阿兹特克帝国。一位年轻的阿兹特克男孩在父亲被西班牙征服者杀害后逃往特诺奇蒂特兰。他在蝙蝠神 Tzinacan 的神庙中训练，并研制武器为父复仇。一路上，他遇到了一些为人熟知的人物，比如美洲豹女侠和征服者埃尔南·科尔特斯。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"蝙蝠俠：阿茲特克帝國之戰","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"在這個大膽重塑的《蝙蝠俠》傳奇中，背景設定於阿茲特克帝國。一名年輕的阿茲特克男孩在父親被西班牙征服者殺害後逃往特諾奇提特蘭。他在蝙蝠神的神殿中接受訓練並研發武器，只為替父報仇。旅途中，他遇見了熟悉的角色，例如美洲豹之女以及西班牙征服者赫南·科爾特斯。"},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"TW","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Ацтекский Бэтмен: Столкновение империй","runtime":0,"tagline":"«Новая История»","homepage":"","overview":"Времена Ацтекской империи, история мальчика по имени Йоуалли Коатль, который переживает страшную утрату: его отец и вождь поселения Толтекацин убит испанскими конкистадорами. Ведомый местью и желанием защитить свой народ от захватчиков, Йоуалли обустраивает храм бога летучих мышей Цинакана в качестве логова и начинает тренировки со своим наставником Акатцином, попутно разрабатывая оружие и снаряжение."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"Batman Aztec: Đế Chế Huyết Chiến","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Phim kể về Yohualli Coatl, một chàng trai Aztec trẻ tuổi, người chứng kiến cha mình — Toltecatzin — bị quân viễn chinh Tây Ban Nha giết hại. Lớn lên, Yohualli trở thành linh mục dưới triều vua Moctezuma II, đồng thời bí mật sử dụng thân phận siêu anh hùng “Batman”. Hắn được huấn luyện tại đền của thần dơi Tzinacan, chế tạo vũ khí và thiết bị để chống"},"name":"Tiếng Việt","iso_639_1":"vi","iso_3166_1":"VN","english_name":"Vietnamese"},{"data":{"title":"Actekų Betmenas: Imperijų susidūrimas","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Actekų imperijos laikais jaunuolis išgyvena tragediją, kai jo tėvas nužudomas ispanų konkistadorų. Siekdamas perspėti karalių ir aukščiausiąjį žynį apie gresiantį pavojų, jis bėga į didingąją sostinę, kur šventykloje, skirtoje šikšnosparnių dievui, mokosi kovos meno ir kuria unikalią įrangą bei ginklus.  Treniruočių metu jis sutinka nuožmią kovotoją ir susiduria su negailestingais užkariautojais, siekdamas atkeršyti už tėvo mirtį ir apsaugoti savo tautą nuo pražūties. Epinė kova tarp senovės tradicijų ir naujų užkariautojų jėgų atskleidžia drąsos, išdavystės ir pasiaukojimo istoriją, alsuojančią actekų kultūros paslaptimis ir žiaurios kolonizacijos realybe."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"באטמן האצטקי: התנגשות אימפריות","runtime":89,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"ילד אצטקי צעיר חווה טרגדיה כאשר אביו נרצח על ידי כובשים ספרדים. יוהואלי נמלט לטנוצ'טיטלן כדי להזהיר את המלך מוקטזומה ואת הכהן הגדול שלו, יוקה, מפני סכנה קרובה."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":1202107,"adult":false,"title":"Amityville Apt.","video":false,"overview":"Forty years after the infamous house was destroyed, the town has built an apartment complex on the same property. Strange occurrences and disturbances start happening at each of the residences.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8405,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/b8wgVO5noXPQAIvm2HJfisdcOOr.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-14","vote_average":2,"backdrop_path":"/rzwlJQzg7wru6upgeIpUOx2xpfO.jpg","original_title":"Amityville Apt.","original_language":"en"},{"id":1374462,"adult":false,"title":"A Woman Called Mother","video":false,"overview":"After her father’s death, Vira’s mother has a mental breakdown. To start fresh, the family moves to a new city and opens a hair salon together. While the family attempts to adjust to their new lives, Vira’s mother, Yanti, begins exhibiting strange, violent behavior reminiscent of her mental breakdown and becomes particularly preoccupied with her son’s sex life. Vira begins to investigate the strange occurrences and discovers that a dangerous ritual and a demonic possession are just the tip of the iceberg.","genre_ids":[27,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.3032,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/pfg4iuS1lgDaZxPgNDsWbhTfqin.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-25","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/2Ap7h6JUagkDwK4Mrt3PlmuAndB.jpg","original_title":"Dia Bukan Ibu","original_language":"id"},{"id":138505,"adult":false,"title":"Demons of Eden","video":false,"overview":"Documentary that focuses on the story of journalist Lydia Cacho, in which her fight against the network of pedophiles she has revealed is discussed. The film follows the difficult process followed to confront the powerful businessmen and politicians who protect and surround those involved in these crimes: a child pornography network operating in Cancun and the United States.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0797,"vote_count":4,"poster_path":"/f75gmu1S2GeqgEm5GJpBccApJY3.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-12","vote_average":5.75,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Los demonios del Edén","original_language":"es"},{"id":1120622,"adult":false,"title":"The Shadow Out of Time","video":false,"overview":"In 1908 Nathaniel Wingate Peaslee, a university professor, suffers a sudden mental breakdown during a class. In 1913 he seems to recover but has no memory of the last five years. He sets out to discover what happened.","genre_ids":[53,27,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0859,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/cD61peEjEk5BUOix1RcQMcA1vtO.jpg","release_date":"2012-03-30","vote_average":4,"backdrop_path":"/qa7uZ36fujHKacXYnXmu1VEZtWO.jpg","original_title":"The Shadow Out of Time","original_language":"en"},{"id":472027,"adult":false,"title":"Batman: The Dark Knight Returns","video":true,"overview":"Batman has not been seen for ten years. A new breed of criminal ravages Gotham City, forcing fifty-five-year-old Bruce Wayne back into the cape and cowl, but does he still have what it takes to fight crime in a new era?","genre_ids":[16,28,9648,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.9242,"vote_count":154,"poster_path":"/g1CECBSnaASE2jeyQdPhcnZqiHm.jpg","release_date":"2013-10-08","vote_average":8.146,"backdrop_path":"/aAp0AkCBsMUDFCuLyd3MTcJ6ZV5.jpg","original_title":"Batman: The Dark Knight Returns","original_language":"en"},{"id":1422096,"adult":false,"title":"Good Boy","video":false,"overview":"A loyal dog moves to a rural family home with his owner Todd, only to discover supernatural forces lurking in the shadows. As dark entities threaten his human companion, the brave pup must fight to protect the one he loves most.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.0415,"vote_count":524,"poster_path":"/daInKxjoRNLFWIus64fHAy91V0k.jpg","release_date":"2025-10-01","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/mPtPJzBkwksUoMEKpkZqxBrlKpZ.jpg","original_title":"Good Boy","original_language":"en"},{"id":710258,"adult":false,"title":"Rust","video":false,"overview":"Infamous outlaw Harland Rust breaks his estranged grandson Lucas out of prison, after Lucas is convicted to hang for an accidental murder. The two must outrun legendary U.S Marshal Wood Helm and bounty hunter Fenton \"Preacher\" Lang who are hot on their tails. Deeply buried secrets rise from the ashes and an unexpected familial bond begins to form as the mismatched duo tries to survive the merciless American Frontier.","genre_ids":[37,28,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1335,"vote_count":142,"poster_path":"/tbJ3RkA2s6X5qrBzrYHYTxvDBui.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-01","vote_average":6.8,"backdrop_path":"/12tEzU0bNYKIjXXEwI5abuOotHF.jpg","original_title":"Rust","original_language":"en"},{"id":13494,"adult":false,"title":"Red Sonja","video":false,"overview":"A young girl rises from the ashes of tragedy to become the most feared warrior woman of all time: the She-Devil with a Sword.","genre_ids":[12,28,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.3722,"vote_count":192,"poster_path":"/aE3yh4y0h96CZZpLo0UDFMWZAA9.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-31","vote_average":5.737,"backdrop_path":"/xSD0q1FiuZkvHuy7uscOLbmd1hR.jpg","original_title":"Red Sonja","original_language":"en"},{"id":1246049,"adult":false,"title":"Dracula","video":false,"overview":"In late 15th-century Eastern Europe, Prince Vlad II’s bride is brutally murdered. As a result, he renounces God and damns Heaven itself. Cursed with eternal life, Vlad is reborn as Dracula, an immortal warlord who defies fate in a blood-soaked crusade to wrench his lost love back from death.","genre_ids":[27,14,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":42.8901,"vote_count":883,"poster_path":"/libhghrUSBSEdHgF9uP1SQES0nQ.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-30","vote_average":7.127,"backdrop_path":"/be5SIsRGMckO8tU9lrLcIik70Dy.jpg","original_title":"Dracula","original_language":"fr"},{"id":604079,"adult":false,"title":"The Long Walk","video":false,"overview":"In a dystopian near-future America, fifty teenage boys take part in a deadly annual walking contest, forced to maintain a minimum pace or be executed, until only one survivor remains.","genre_ids":[878,27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":13.8659,"vote_count":1175,"poster_path":"/wobVTa99eW0ht6c1rNNzLkazPtR.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-10","vote_average":6.948,"backdrop_path":"/o0Id62Wx3gjYMHunJV96WAOspN.jpg","original_title":"The Long Walk","original_language":"en"},{"id":2661,"adult":false,"title":"Batman","video":false,"overview":"The Dynamic Duo faces four super-villains who plan to hold the world for ransom with the help of a secret invention that instantly dehydrates people.","genre_ids":[28,35,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.8685,"vote_count":1037,"poster_path":"/zzoPxWHnPa0eyfkMLgwbNvdEcVF.jpg","release_date":"1966-07-30","vote_average":6.396,"backdrop_path":"/s2JJkEcVz1Q4uLnNhWZwCcBjqMr.jpg","original_title":"Batman","original_language":"en"},{"id":617126,"adult":false,"title":"The Fantastic 4: First Steps","video":false,"overview":"Against the vibrant backdrop of a 1960s-inspired, retro-futuristic world, Marvel's First Family is forced to balance their roles as heroes with the strength of their family bond, while defending Earth from a ravenous space god called Galactus and his enigmatic Herald, Silver Surfer.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.8624,"vote_count":3016,"poster_path":"/nf5qaSEvyYSNeFH0YhSs5EsBLX9.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-23","vote_average":6.97,"backdrop_path":"/s94NjfKkcSczZ1FembwmQZwsuwY.jpg","original_title":"The Fantastic 4: First Steps","original_language":"en"},{"id":9618,"adult":false,"title":"Tango & Cash","video":false,"overview":"Ray Tango and Gabriel Cash are two successful narcotics detectives who can't stand each other. Crime lord Yves Perret, furious at the loss of income they have caused him, plots an elaborate revenge against them.","genre_ids":[28,53,35,18,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.3969,"vote_count":2076,"poster_path":"/jxxxjTu87OSmQYkMFF7MgOEDXRn.jpg","release_date":"1989-12-22","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/vzvHhP8ZrDvOOx5fa9YC0OzDNIU.jpg","original_title":"Tango & Cash","original_language":"en"},{"id":23202,"adult":false,"title":"Trick 'r Treat","video":false,"overview":"Four interwoven stories that occur on Halloween: an everyday high school principal has a secret life as a serial killer; a college virgin might have just met the one guy for her; a group of teenagers pull a mean prank, and a bitter old recluse receives an uninvited guest.","genre_ids":[27,35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.1958,"vote_count":2026,"poster_path":"/w0nmol4g7n6MFfhfphV7GzHHYjB.jpg","release_date":"2007-12-09","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/wYI3r4DGKhwjPoDpfPfGdLMrPLt.jpg","original_title":"Trick 'r Treat","original_language":"en"},{"id":1356039,"adult":false,"title":"Counterattack","video":false,"overview":"When a hostage rescue mission creates a new enemy, Capt. Guerrero and his elite soldiers must face an ambush by a criminal group.","genre_ids":[28,12,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.5195,"vote_count":785,"poster_path":"/38I76hGcFY6xB47pjm7pZwkfuAF.jpg","release_date":"2025-02-27","vote_average":8.262,"backdrop_path":"/deUWVEgNh2IGjShyymZhaYP40ye.jpg","original_title":"Contraataque","original_language":"es"},{"id":1007734,"adult":false,"title":"Nobody 2","video":false,"overview":"Former assassin Hutch Mansell takes his family on a nostalgic vacation to a small-town theme park, only to be pulled back into violence when they clash with a corrupt operator, a crooked sheriff, and a ruthless crime boss.","genre_ids":[28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":17.7032,"vote_count":1279,"poster_path":"/iyxwxDZCpIm0vIORaHpmgJv2BGF.jpg","release_date":"2025-08-13","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/82C04rTiXYZ7c8XZv91Nu53w82Y.jpg","original_title":"Nobody 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":1376434,"adult":false,"title":"Predator: Killer of Killers","video":false,"overview":"While three of the fiercest warriors in human history—a Viking raider, a ninja in feudal Japan, and a WWII pilot—are killers in their own right, they are merely prey for their new opponent: the ultimate killer of killers.","genre_ids":[16,28,878,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.5185,"vote_count":1099,"poster_path":"/2XDQa6EmFHSA37j1t0w88vpWqj9.jpg","release_date":"2025-06-05","vote_average":7.822,"backdrop_path":"/3AGZKVr2DPT9H53gYtkSEC1tK1E.jpg","original_title":"Predator: Killer of Killers","original_language":"en"},{"id":274854,"adult":false,"title":"The Last Witch Hunter","video":false,"overview":"The modern world holds many secrets, but by far the most astounding is that witches still live among us; vicious supernatural creatures intent on unleashing the Black Death upon the world and putting an end to the human race once and for all. Armies of witch hunters have battled this unnatural enemy for centuries, including Kaulder, a valiant warrior who many years ago slayed the all-powerful Witch Queen, decimating her followers in the process. In the moments right before her death, the Queen cursed Kaulder with immortality, forever separating him from his beloved wife and daughter. Today, Kaulder is the last living hunter who has spent his immortal life tracking down rogue witches, all the while yearning for his long-lost family.","genre_ids":[28,12,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.5489,"vote_count":3792,"poster_path":"/dS9YdnJkxtKE2PKCSsxTaO7Jpf5.jpg","release_date":"2015-10-21","vote_average":6.011,"backdrop_path":"/mXmvN6drkdU1PWFF92AGklEVIa3.jpg","original_title":"The Last Witch Hunter","original_language":"en"},{"id":346910,"adult":false,"title":"The Predator","video":false,"overview":"When a young boy accidentally triggers the universe's most lethal hunters' return to Earth, only a ragtag crew of ex-soldiers and a disgruntled scientist can prevent the end of the human race.","genre_ids":[878,28,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":9.8833,"vote_count":5042,"poster_path":"/a3eWGF6YPF7No5Rbtjc8QpDvz7l.jpg","release_date":"2018-09-05","vote_average":5.63,"backdrop_path":"/zGHdS1eLaU5wdYCJ6vY9QfQGCTo.jpg","original_title":"The Predator","original_language":"en"},{"id":575265,"adult":false,"title":"Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning","video":false,"overview":"Ethan Hunt and team continue their search for the terrifying AI known as the Entity — which has infiltrated intelligence networks all over the globe — with the world's governments and a mysterious ghost from Hunt's past on their trail. Joined by new allies and armed with the means to shut the Entity down for good, Hunt is in a race against time to prevent the world as we know it from changing forever.","genre_ids":[28,53,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":39.368,"vote_count":2581,"poster_path":"/z53D72EAOxGRqdr7KXXWp9dJiDe.jpg","release_date":"2025-05-17","vote_average":7.19,"backdrop_path":"/538U9snNc2fpnOmYXAPUh3zn31H.jpg","original_title":"Mission: Impossible - The Final Reckoning","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":75,"adult":false,"title":"Mars Attacks!","video":false,"overview":"A fleet of Martian spacecraft surrounds the world's major cities and all of humanity waits to see if the extraterrestrial visitors have, as they claim, \"come in peace.\" U.S. President James Dale receives assurance from science professor Donald Kessler that the Martians' mission is a friendly one. But when a peaceful exchange ends in the total annihilation of the U.S. Congress, military men call for a full-scale nuclear retaliation.","genre_ids":[35,14,878],"popularity":5.384,"vote_count":5781,"poster_path":"/hll4O5vSAfnZDb6JbnP06GPtz7b.jpg","release_date":"1996-12-13","vote_average":6.4,"backdrop_path":"/ELsTifJ2lu4vsMhoHeZ5EnncHw.jpg","original_title":"Mars Attacks!","original_language":"en"},{"id":272,"adult":false,"title":"Batman Begins","video":false,"overview":"Driven by tragedy, billionaire Bruce Wayne dedicates his life to uncovering and defeating the corruption that plagues his home, Gotham City.  Unable to work within the system, he instead creates a new identity, a symbol of fear for the criminal underworld - The Batman.","genre_ids":[18,80,28],"popularity":12.5976,"vote_count":22281,"poster_path":"/sPX89Td70IDDjVr85jdSBb4rWGr.jpg","release_date":"2005-06-10","vote_average":7.721,"backdrop_path":"/9IIBboV7MCT0bTxzXHmWK1Hq558.jpg","original_title":"Batman Begins","original_language":"en"},{"id":1724,"adult":false,"title":"The Incredible Hulk","video":false,"overview":"Scientist Bruce Banner scours the planet for an antidote to the unbridled force of rage within him: the Hulk. But when the military masterminds who dream of exploiting his powers force him back to civilization, he finds himself coming face to face with a new, deadly foe.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":10.6929,"vote_count":12500,"poster_path":"/gKzYx79y0AQTL4UAk1cBQJ3nvrm.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-12","vote_average":6.231,"backdrop_path":"/jPu8yiadqgzwFPGKJmGo637ASVP.jpg","original_title":"The Incredible Hulk","original_language":"en"},{"id":1726,"adult":false,"title":"Iron Man","video":false,"overview":"After being held captive in an Afghan cave, billionaire engineer Tony Stark creates a unique weaponized suit of armor to fight evil.","genre_ids":[28,878,12],"popularity":18.753,"vote_count":27782,"poster_path":"/78lPtwv72eTNqFW9COBYI0dWDJa.jpg","release_date":"2008-04-30","vote_average":7.655,"backdrop_path":"/cKvDv2LpwVEqbdXWoQl4XgGN6le.jpg","original_title":"Iron Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":1771,"adult":false,"title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","video":false,"overview":"During World War II, Steve Rogers is a sickly man from Brooklyn who's transformed into super-soldier Captain America to aid in the war effort. Rogers must stop the Red Skull – Adolf Hitler's ruthless head of weaponry, and the leader of an organization that intends to use a mysterious device of untold powers for world domination.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":7.3077,"vote_count":22477,"poster_path":"/vSNxAJTlD0r02V9sPYpOjqDZXUK.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-22","vote_average":7.004,"backdrop_path":"/yFuKvT4Vm3sKHdFY4eG6I4ldAnn.jpg","original_title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","original_language":"en"},{"id":1979,"adult":false,"title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","video":false,"overview":"The Fantastic Four return to the big screen as a new and all powerful enemy threatens the Earth. The seemingly unstoppable 'Silver Surfer', but all is not what it seems and there are old and new enemies that pose a greater threat than the intrepid superheroes realize.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"popularity":6.028,"vote_count":8294,"poster_path":"/1rxTraSO45jbvTrCeSvJ6RmOu1b.jpg","release_date":"2007-06-13","vote_average":5.63,"backdrop_path":"/o2wYH40zW0JIYiYUTu6L4gsNy7E.jpg","original_title":"Fantastic Four: Rise of the Silver Surfer","original_language":"en"},{"id":2000,"adult":false,"title":"Aguirre, the Wrath of God","video":false,"overview":"A few decades after the destruction of the Inca Empire, a Spanish expedition led by the infamous Aguirre leaves the mountains of Peru and goes down the Amazon River in search of the lost city of El Dorado. When great difficulties arise, Aguirre’s men start to wonder whether their quest will lead them to prosperity or certain death.","genre_ids":[36,12,18],"popularity":2.0103,"vote_count":1210,"poster_path":"/qMk93yMo82svW27FEjudgueBMUL.jpg","release_date":"1972-12-29","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/kfSZaOr9ApNR52gWKlpXHD0id0W.jpg","original_title":"Aguirre, der Zorn Gottes","original_language":"de"},{"id":1061474,"adult":false,"title":"Superman","video":false,"overview":"Superman, a journalist in Metropolis, embarks on a journey to reconcile his Kryptonian heritage with his human upbringing as Clark Kent.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"popularity":28.4139,"vote_count":4375,"poster_path":"/ldyfo0BKmz5rWtJJKCvwaNS4cJT.jpg","release_date":"2025-07-09","vote_average":7.358,"backdrop_path":"/aJDLz1748CIMZkCkyISYe5Hl6I7.jpg","original_title":"Superman","original_language":"en"},{"id":2055,"adult":false,"title":"Open Range","video":false,"overview":"A former gunslinger is forced to take up arms again when he and his cattle crew are threatened by a corrupt lawman.","genre_ids":[37,18,28],"popularity":3.7138,"vote_count":1173,"poster_path":"/1mrNc88NrUEGtMtat4FD7sfpFrW.jpg","release_date":"2003-08-11","vote_average":7.222,"backdrop_path":"/e65E7jH5bKMSgHJnWLw4ex02Dyu.jpg","original_title":"Open Range","original_language":"en"},{"id":1924,"adult":false,"title":"Superman","video":false,"overview":"Mild-mannered Clark Kent works as a reporter at the Daily Planet alongside his crush, Lois Lane. Clark must summon his superhero alter-ego when the nefarious Lex Luthor launches a plan to take over the world.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":6.9771,"vote_count":4183,"poster_path":"/d7px1FQxW4tngdACVRsCSaZq0Xl.jpg","release_date":"1978-12-14","vote_average":7.154,"backdrop_path":"/p2zBTOd4JdmNhkRWHmjKg7hk3s1.jpg","original_title":"Superman","original_language":"en"},{"id":1927,"adult":false,"title":"Hulk","video":false,"overview":"Bruce Banner, a genetics researcher with a tragic past, suffers massive radiation exposure in his laboratory that causes him to transform into a raging green monster when he gets angry.","genre_ids":[878,12,28],"popularity":8.3228,"vote_count":6180,"poster_path":"/UllIft2jLSBaay3zQyMV4GNdfy.jpg","release_date":"2003-06-19","vote_average":5.579,"backdrop_path":"/8vQBXqDbb30qNpBcNYwTesSg75.jpg","original_title":"Hulk","original_language":"en"},{"id":1930,"adult":false,"title":"The Amazing Spider-Man","video":false,"overview":"Peter Parker is an outcast high schooler abandoned by his parents as a boy, leaving him to be raised by his Uncle Ben and Aunt May. Like most teenagers, Peter is trying to figure out who he is and how he got to be the person he is today. As Peter discovers a mysterious briefcase that belonged to his father, he begins a quest to understand his parents' disappearance – leading him directly to Oscorp and the lab of Dr. Curt Connors, his father's former partner. As Spider-Man is set on a collision course with Connors' alter ego, The Lizard, Peter will make life-altering choices to use his powers and shape his destiny to become a hero.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":15.874,"vote_count":18266,"poster_path":"/jexoNYnPd6vVrmygwF6QZmWPFdu.jpg","release_date":"2012-06-23","vote_average":6.727,"backdrop_path":"/HVcza6tJtWFrLriuh3Ano4Vt46.jpg","original_title":"The Amazing Spider-Man","original_language":"en"},{"id":276175,"adult":false,"title":"The Treasure of Moctezuma","video":false,"overview":"Santo and Jorge Rivero team-up to stop an international syndicate from stealing Mexico's greatest treasure.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.2126,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/3ZOEq7FeIDsFB3NpMG0BX8ZzKBe.jpg","release_date":"1968-07-04","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/ta0WSKsmm70SztVY6zFIk0FNXQq.jpg","original_title":"El tesoro de Moctezuma","original_language":"es"},{"id":1064486,"adult":false,"title":"Memoir of a Snail","video":false,"overview":"Forcibly separated from her twin brother when they are orphaned, a melancholic misfit learns how to find confidence within herself amid the