here he remained lost for over sixty years. But now, with the world facing the very same evil, Captain America must rise again as our last hope for survival.","genre_ids":[28,16,10751,12,878],"popularity":2.0601,"vote_count":386,"poster_path":"/iMCkGHVrYRdqKROPRPmVaJVSlg3.jpg","release_date":"2006-02-21","vote_average":6.863,"backdrop_path":"/lJRGgbi4Slsz171vcJ0Ctgiea6v.jpg","original_title":"Ultimate Avengers: The Movie","original_language":"en"},{"id":14611,"adult":false,"title":"Ultimate Avengers 2","video":false,"overview":"Mysterious Wakanda lies in the darkest heart of Africa, unknown to most of the world. An isolated land hidden behind closed borders, fiercely protected by its young king: Black Panther. But when brutal alien invaders attack, the threat leaves Black Panther with no option but to go against the sacred decrees of his people and ask for help from outsiders.","genre_ids":[12,16,28,878],"popularity":1.5956,"vote_count":317,"poster_path":"/sMFyYZR9krqcQC99G6jnb10Zv4P.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-08","vote_average":6.803,"backdrop_path":"/hoJpIYgFPc75NhaSWPNUeMFPMy1.jpg","original_title":"Ultimate Avengers 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":14613,"adult":false,"title":"Next Avengers: Heroes of Tomorrow","video":false,"overview":"The children of the Avengers hone their powers and go head to head with the very enemy responsible for their parents' demise.","genre_ids":[16,10751,28,12,878],"popularity":1.3342,"vote_count":303,"poster_path":"/1y4J9HZJoTIMdt77wCq80uXaQJ.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-02","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/6V6rhHkqYvJGlxIQ9mvZuIoY6c9.jpg","original_title":"Next Avengers: Heroes of Tomorrow","original_language":"en"},{"id":14696,"adult":false,"title":"Ugetsu","video":false,"overview":"In 16th century Japan, peasants Genjuro and Tobei sell their earthenware pots to a group of soldiers in a nearby village, in defiance of a local sage's warning against seeking to profit from warfare. Genjuro's pursuit of both riches and the mysterious Lady Wakasa, as well as Tobei's desire to become a samurai, run the risk of destroying both themselves and their wives, Miyagi and Ohama.","genre_ids":[14,18,9648],"popularity":2.7814,"vote_count":628,"poster_path":"/r8RiuKTIYIJBjczBVsfeP5C00CJ.jpg","release_date":"1953-03-26","vote_average":8.005,"backdrop_path":"/iB1tCWl4MKl6OO1kMBD5LxM5BmJ.jpg","original_title":"雨月物語","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt21110654","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q130267916","instagram_id":null},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148500,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"AS","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""},{"note":"HBO Max","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-12-21T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"AU","release_dates":[{"note":"HBO Max","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-19T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"M"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-19T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"16"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"CO","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-18T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","release_dates":[{"note":"HBO Max","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-19T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"GB","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-22T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"15"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"GU","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":4,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"2025-09-19T00:00:00